20 miles over the limit.
-Just please!

07:52.138 --> 07:53.973
-(text whooshes)
-It's fine.

07:54.056 --> 07:55.892
Well, I mean,
do you wanna get a ticket?
Do you want that?

07:55.975 --> 07:58.936
-You have to get a little
thing on your license.
-(sighs)

07:59.020 --> 08:00.479
