get this over with.

08:02.607 --> 08:05.735
Mary Jo:
You can just drop me
and go off and have your fun.

08:05.818 --> 08:08.362
(laughs) Yeah...

08:08.446 --> 08:11.032
I'm having a great time.
Trish, you having fun?

08:11.115 --> 08:12.575
Oh, my God, so fun.

08:13.784 --> 08:15.786
I wanna go home,

08:15.870 --> 08:17.288
but you won't let me.

08:17.371 --> 08:19.832
Won't let you?
What are you talking about?

08:19.916 --> 08:21.667
You know, Mom,
this is not our fault.

08:21.751 --> 08:23.127
